| form | the catastrophic cancellation | global lattice |
|---|---|---|
| **c1 = (R²−1)+c** (Sterbenz-blessed) | `R²−1` **operation-EXACT, 32/32 cells** (greedy/local optimum) | **{−0.5…0.5} HALF lattice — worse** |
